title: DivX Media Converter + Serial Code
description:
Introduction
+===============-

   Convert to DivX in one step

   The DivX(r) Converter allows you to convert nearly any digital
   video into a DivX media file in one step. Why would you want
   to do that? Well, the DivX Media Format can change the way you
   play,create and share digital video.

   Converting your videos to DivX video files can be done in one
   easy step. Simply drag and drop your videos onto the DivX
   Converter, choose a DivX profile setting and click ?Convert.?
   That?s it ? you?re done. Admittedly, that may sound like more
   than one step, but it?s really just one three-pronged step. Or
   maybe it?s one full step followed by two small ?baby-steps.?
   Anyway, it?s really, really easy to create a DivX video.


  System Requirements
+======================-

   PIV 1Ghz or better
   Windows 2000, XP or Vista
   DirectX 9
   64MB RAM
   20MB free space for application
